{"tid":1652743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【討論post】幫支那火上加油 要支那抵制埋俄國斯呢個靠山","createTime":"2019-10-13T19:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T19:12:36.000Z","uid":209850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e3339b268bd9893c8aa1238892600a99b993424b","tid":1652743,"uid":209850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:12:36.000Z","msg":"講左幾個月將革命輸出番支那成效都係唔多明顯<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，唯有玩另一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班支那人咁愛國成日屌鳩我地港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話中國領土一點都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁作為連登仔就一於借力打力，利用班支那既愛國心向俄國斯開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講番比啲支那人知中國領土比俄羅斯吞併左幾多，我地作為正義既一方緊係要幫國家奪回領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">試下打着紅旗反紅旗，攞正牌幫支共增添麻煩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要搞砸支共先要令佢國際間孤立佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一黎可以令支共冇左俄仔呢個重要靠山<br />\n二黎班五毛唔得閒搞我地 要應付國內輿論<br />\n<br />\n真係搞得成要支共人民同俄羅斯反面，真係諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry for 1999<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keOrZKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeOrZKY.jpg&h=d9a6c954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQpSaRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQpSaRE.jpg&h=000e7063&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}